One way of summarising resulting distributions is through boxplots:

~\\

<<hist-simp-9, fig.height=2.0>>=
par(mai=cmai)
plot(xvalslog, yvalslog, col="red", lwd=3,
     xlim=range(xvalslog), ylim = c(0, 0.03), type="l",
